Things needed to run a simulation:

1.  Driver script (trivial).
2.  SimulationController
3.  Pylith solver derives from Pyre class Solver.
3.1  Implement Solver interface in Pylith.
3.1.1 launch
3.1.2 applyBoundaryConditions
3.1.3 newStep
3.1.4 advance
optional:  save, begin/endSimulation, begin/endTimeStep
4.  Separate from SimulationController:
    _configure
    _init
    _fini (do nothing)
